_json.gridTitle: Cinnamon Swirl Grain-Free Bread (Paleo, GAPS, SCD, grain-free, dairy-free, refined sugar-free)
_json.description: CINNAMON SWIRL BREAD. Gluten-free, Grain-free. PALEO, PRIMAL and SCD, GAPs I put this on the dessert board since this is such a treat. There is no way you miss wheat eating this! It is delicious! 4 large eggs, room temp 1/2c almond butter & apple sauce (unsweetened) 1tsp apple cider vinegar 3Tbsp honey or maple syrup 1Tbsp vanilla  2Tbsp olive oil 2tsp cinnamon 1 3/4 cup blanched almond flour 1/2 tsp salt 3/4 tsp baking soda 1/2 Tbsp cinnamon 1/4 cup coconut sugar (2Tbsp honey)
